content: Léo Andéol is a second-year master student at École Normale Supérieure Paris-Saclay. He received his bachelor degree in Computer Science from Université Paris-Dauphine in 2018. He is currently an intern at RIKEN, at the Tokyo Institute of Technology. He is interested in machine learning and optimization. Before that, he was a Bachelor student in Computer Science at Université Paris-Dauphine.
